headline: FlexShares® Announces Liquidation of an Exchange Traded Fund
summary: CHICAGO, October 02, 2025--Northern Trust’s FlexShares Exchange Traded Funds announced the liquidation and termination of the FlexShares Real Assets Allocation Index Fund (Ticker: ASET) (the "Fund"). Prior to and through the close of regular trading (the "Close of Trading") on the Nasdaq Stock Market LLC ("Nasdaq") on or about October 20, 2025 (the "Closing Date"), the Fund will undertake the process of closing down and liquidating its portfolio.
